				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There ii no way to reset your pets size once you shrink it now. I even went and picked up a Anizoh's Maximizing Device and it only works on me, not my pet even when I target him.
<br />

<br />
Full sized pets can fight at max melee better than a small pet will. I'm not asking for anything more than a way to make the pet revert back to regualr size or larger if he will fight at a greater range like melee people will.
<br />

<br />
