We were in a joint Fen Ro raid getting some back flags for members. Some jackoff necro turned FRo in to a skeleton for a little while, well it screwed up melee range ans people walked in closer from max melee. 2/3 of the melee people died because of the change in size of the Mob.
<br />

<br />
With this in mind, I watched how different sized pets would fight at different ranges. On the Warlord in PoEb with AE ramp I have had a pet live when full sized vs shrunk. I don't have parses to back up anything. It's a personal feel more than anything. I've had pets live vs RZ in time when full sized when shrunk they get WTF owned.
<br />

<br />
Sorry I hadn't responded earlier, I thought I had but I must have screwed up. Again, I'm not asking for ground backing powers for Pet Classes. Once a pet is shrunk, I know of no way to unshrink it.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=707977">Quilin</a> of Lanys
<br />
D.S.P.S. Double Secret Probation  Society
